{"tid":1994813,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣外賣仔增至4間(茶匠&巴巴站&咖啡灣&burgerland)","createTime":"2020-04-29T18:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T08:20:00.000Z","uid":145118,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"390c183bf8ca9a73abaeb58baa7bdffbbd55717a","tid":1994813,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T18:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好消息！<br />\n<br />\n外賣仔將新增以下餐廳既外賣服務：<br />\nBurgerland（合單優惠A區）、<br />\nBaba&rsquo;s station（A區）、<br />\n茶匠（A區）、<br />\n咖啡灣（B區）。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鑒於唔少朋友反映QR code「唔係咁易掃」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以依家可以係wtsapp落單熱線查看餐單啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有夠方便的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外賣仔明白自己有好多不足之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我地一定會不斷改進 越做越好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊亦會繼續搜羅荃灣特色小店，為大家送上美食佳餚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快d Whatsapp 61469599 嗌外賣懲罰我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tsuenwanyodelivery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftsuenwanyodelivery&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=bcbdc141\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tsuenwanyodelivery</a>"},{"pid":"4e1055a291c2cd84197095a5ef463e83d2ea4412